dct_title_s: Survey of beach channel at Ship Bottom Beach, Arlington, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: This map shows Ship Bottom Beach, Arlington, and its streets and railroad. It also appears to show water depth information and sounding measurements. The map is a mimeo with attached Xerox copy.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Additional information is faintly handwritten and is not clearly legible.
